(1154,	209,	'_s1_heading',	'field_5dca3af614de6'),
(1155,	209,	's1_text',	'A group of committed Mum’s recognised that vitamins and nutritional supplements for Australian Mum’s were lagging the current health guidelines and global research. To ensure Australian Mum’s had access to the latest ingredients and optimal vitamin blends we launched Forever Mum. The Forever Mum team of naturopaths, pharmacists, dieticians, doctors and wellness coaches work together to guarantee we deliver on our promise to you, to ‘to support you at every stage of the pregnancy journey’. Forever Mum is 100% Australian owned and operated.'),
