(4195,	386,	'main_content',	'<p>Planning a family is an exciting decision! The formulation of <strong>Forever Mum Her Conceive</strong> is based on latest knowledge of key nutrients to support your journey to become a mum. Recent breakthroughs help our understanding of the role key nutrients can play in preparing the body for pregnancy and supporting health. <strong>Forever Mum Her Conceive</strong> combines key antioxidants including Vitamin C and Zinc, with Active B Vitamins, choline, iodine, and Quatrefolic™- the next generation of Folic Acid. Together, they help prepare your body for pregnancy, support preconception health and maintain reproductive system health– ready for baby!</p>\r\n<p>Folic Acid helps prevent neural tube defects such as spina bifida when trying to conceive and during the first trimester of pregnancy.</p>\r\n<p>Antioxidants reduce free radicals produced in the body Active B Vitamins Quatrefolic™ and active B12 are ‘body ready’ for absorption.</p> \r\n<p>Choline supports nervous system health for future mums (as well as) Iodine and Selenium support healthy thyroid hormones</p>'),
(4196,	386,	'_main_content',	'field_5dd2332de1dfd'),
(4197,	386,	'pointers',	'<!--<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Quatrefolic (Activate Folic Acid) -</strong> Activated and naturally occurring for ready absorption* Helps product against neural tube defects such as spina bifida when trying to conceive and during the first trimester of pregnancy.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Choline -</strong> Supports healthy foetal brain and nervous system development, healthy pregnancy, and maternal health.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Antioxidants -</strong> Reduce free radicals produced in the body</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Activated B Vitamins -</strong> Activated B6 and B12 are ‘body ready’ and morebio available</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Iodine -</strong> An essential mineral supporting baby’s brain and nerve development.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>-->'),
(4198,	386,	'_pointers',	'field_5dd23343e1dfe'),
(4199,	386,	'content',	'<p><strong>DIRECTIONS:</strong> Adults- Take 1 soft gel daily with food, or as advised by your healthcare professional.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Warnings: *Do not take with any other Folic Acid supplement unless under medical advice. Once you conceive, we recommend you switch to\r\nForever Mum Pre-conception & Pregnancy Multivitamin.</strong> Advise your doctor of any medicine you take during pregnancy, particularly in your first trimester. If you have had a baby with a neural tube defect/spina bifida - seek specific medical advice. Do not exceed the stated dose except on medical advice. This product contains Selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 micrograms for adults of Selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Store below 25°C. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.</p>\r\n'),
