(4429,	387,	'main_content',	'<p>Whether starting a family or adding to the tribe, <strong>Forever Mum Pre-Conception + Pregnancy Multivitamin</strong> is designed to support a healthy pregnancy journey for all mums. With great care, our prenatal multi is formulated with a broad range of selected nutrients, designed to support maternal health and baby’s healthy foetal development.</p>                                                                                                                                                 <p>It contains 22 nutrients, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Folic acid, which helps to prevent neural tube defects such as spina bifida when trying to conceive and during the first trimester of pregnancy.</li>\r\n<li>Our gentle, tummy-friendly and bioavailable form of iron</li>                                                                                                                                                                                                                           <li>Our active B12 and Quatrefolic (active folate), the “body ready” B vitamins for absorption</li>                                                                         <li>Our specially selected choline</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>                                                                     \r\n\r\n\r\n'),
