(4433,	387,	'content',	'<p><strong>DIRECTIONS:</strong> Adults take 1 soft capsule daily with food or as advised by your healthcare professional.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Warnings:</strong> Advise your doctor of any medicine you take during pregnancy, particularly in your first trimenter.  If you are concerned about the health of yourself or your baby, talk to your health practitioner.  If you have had a baby with a neural tube defect/spina bifida - seek specific medical advice. Do not exceed the stated dose except on medical advice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Store below 25°C. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing</p>\r\n'),
