(6374,	672,	's2_text',	'Forever Mum joined the family of Pharmacare brands in 2018. Pharmacare was founded over 30 years ago, in Sydney’s Northern beaches and delivers a wide range of products to consumers in over 40 countries. It is the hub of our research and development with the core mission of improving lives. The Pharmacare brand portfolio spans hundreds of products in key health categories such as health and fitness, personal care and food services and includes household names such as Nature’s Way, Sambucol, Bioglan, Ease-a-Cold, Rosken, and KP-24.'),
